------------------Periodic Table Speller------------------
                An Entirely Useless Program               
----------------------------------------------------------

This program takes any word or phrase and spells it out
using elements of the periodic table.  It depends on
GTK# and .NET 2.0+ on windows and Mono on *nix.

BUILDING
----------------------------------------------------------
It can be built simply by running NAnt on the source
directory

  $ nant

INSTALLING ON WINDOWS
----------------------------------------------------------
Simply run setup.exe
(duh)

INSTALLING ON LINUX
----------------------------------------------------------
  $ make
  $ sudo make install